localmail
---------

Local SMTP/IMAP server for using in testing systems that send mail.

Dependancies:

    twisted 12.0.0, but any recent version should work

To run:

    twistd localmail --imap <port> --smtp <port>

    (Ports defaults to 2143 for IMAP and 2025 for SMTP)

Alternatively, run via tac file:

    twistd -ny localmail.tac

To test:

    while server is runinng, run "python test.py"
